      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why im still logging into my laptop. the lab results came back today and its just... over. three years of work, the funding is gone, and i feel like there is nothing left of me outside of this research. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for a life that feels like it's constantly breaking. i just want the noise to stop.",
