    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the career though. it feels like when everything else is stripped away, there isn't even a person underneath. i've spent so much energy trying to fix things, trying to make it work, trying to survive the stress... but the stress is the only thing that's actually consistent. i'm just so tired of the cycle. it feels like any real peace would have to be something much bigger than just a \"break\" or a vacation.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
